# GFOS Core - Global Financial Operations Platform

## Overview

Production-grade financial operating system for debt management, payments, installments, ledger accounting, audit trails, and multi-tenant financial operations.

## Technology Stack

- **Frontend**: React + TypeScript (Strict Mode)
- **Backend**: Node.js + Express + TypeScript
- **Database**: PostgreSQL
- **ORM**: Prisma
- **Authentication**: JWT with RBAC
- **Architecture**: DDD + Clean Architecture + Multi-Tenant SaaS

## Core Modules

- Authentication & Authorization
- Customer Management
- Debt Management
- Installment Scheduling
- Payment Processing
- Financial Ledger (Double-Entry Accounting)
- Audit Logs
- Transaction History
- Reporting
- User Management
- Settings Management

## Financial Guarantees

✓ Double-entry accounting foundation  
✓ Immutable audit logs  
✓ ACID-compliant operations  
✓ Atomic payment processing  
✓ Balance reconciliation  
✓ Full transaction traceability  
✓ Soft delete support  
✓ Multi-tenant isolation  

## Project Status

**Current Phase**: Phase 1 - Architecture & Database Design

